Mary Parker (American actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Parker_(American_actress) 0 Mary Parker (born Mary Frances Roberson; August 28, 1918, Fort Worth, Texas – died March 2, 1998, Fort Worth, Texas) was an American stage, television and screen actress/performer. Parker appeared in 17 films from 1938 to 1954, but was also known for her dance work with partner Billy Daniel.
